{"tid":1046793,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"土耳其足球運動員帶刀片入場 暗中划傷對手","createTime":"2019-03-04T13:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T14:36:07.000Z","uid":234938,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f55664535a2d844009b0e8ad3aad2fcffdf26d20","tid":1046793,"uid":234938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"據《Yeni Safak Spor》報道，土耳其阿美德體育俱樂部（Amed S.K.）足球運動員曼蘇爾&middot;查拉爾（Mansur &Ccedil;alar）將刀片悄悄帶入球場，攻擊對方球員。<br />\n<br />\nRT電視台報道稱，此事發生在土耳其乙級聯賽的一場比賽中。查拉爾將刀片藏於手中，幾乎在雙方球員握手問候一結束就開始攻擊對手。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其媒體發佈的視頻顯示，查拉爾攻擊對方球員，後者並未立刻察覺受了刀傷。據媒體消息，他們是在比賽結束後發佈了刀傷照片。<br />\n<br />\n據當地媒體報道，此前曾有針對查拉爾的&quot;骯臟謠言&quot;和污蔑。"},{"pid":"5f091ac28b44c79d3296f61427b6a097e83b6e5a","tid":1046793,"uid":158411,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2113/2113758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2113%2F2113758.jpg&h=1eb205e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"669f95ee1a841576ed92733df8e1e8f0c9273a26","tid":1046793,"uid":234938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m0-XS55rgKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm0-XS55rgKE&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4Mv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=909f49ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m0-XS55rgKE</a>"},{"pid":"21f6179e71e2dafdc70eed65b7d1318a4eef65c8","tid":1046793,"uid":88143,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"如果n賓做球員咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd58b987b80fc9563b599c84ca563c04291d877","tid":1046793,"uid":33527,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"拉條撚樣坐監啦痴撚線<img